# 🚀 Microservices Deployment on AWS EKS

## 📌 Overview
End-to-end DevOps project deploying microservices on AWS EKS using Terraform, Jenkins, Docker, Kubernetes, and monitoring with Prometheus & Grafana.

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack
AWS (EKS, EC2, ECR) • Jenkins • Docker • Kubernetes • Terraform • Prometheus • Grafana

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
GitHub → Jenkins → Docker → ECR → EKS → Application → Grafana

---

## ⚙️ Setup

```bash
# Configure AWS
aws configure

# Create EKS cluster
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply

# Connect to cluster
aws eks update-kubeconfig --region ap-northeast-1 --name your-cluster-name

# Deploy microservices
kubectl apply -f microservices/kubernetes-manifests

# Install monitoring
helm install monitoring prometheus-community/kube-prometheus-stack

